<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-BR">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Guia da Pega</title>
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Fraunces:ital,opsz,wght@0,9..144,400;0,9..144,500;0,9..144,600;0,9..144,700;1,9..144,400;1,9..144,500&family=Quicksand:wght@400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
  :root{
    --branco:#FFFFFF;--rosa-bebe:#FFEAF1;--rosa-claro:#F4D9E4;--rosa-forte:#D94D8C;
    --roxo:#6A3FA0;--roxo-escuro:#4A2A78;--texto-claro:#5A4A6B;--texto-titulo:#4A2A78;
    --verde:#22C55E;--verde-esc:#15A34A;
    --sombra:0 8px 24px rgba(74,42,120,0.08);--sombra-forte:0 14px 40px rgba(74,42,120,0.18);
    --blob:60% 40% 55% 45% / 55% 45% 60% 40%;
  }
  *{margin:0;padding:0;box-sizing:border-box}
  html{scroll-behavior:smooth}
  body{font-family:'Quicksand',sans-serif;color:var(--texto-claro);background:var(--branco);line-height:1.65;font-weight:500;-webkit-font-smoothing:antialiased}
  h1,h2,h3,.serif{font-family:'Fraunces',serif;font-optical-sizing:auto;color:var(--texto-titulo);line-height:1.12;font-weight:600}

  .section{padding:64px 22px}
  .wrap{max-width:1040px;margin:0 auto}
  .narrow{max-width:760px;margin:0 auto}
  .center{text-align:center}

  .eyebrow{font-family:'Quicksand',sans-serif;font-weight:700;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.14em;font-size:.72rem;color:var(--rosa-forte);margin-bottom:14px;display:inline-block}
  .sec-title{font-size:clamp(1.7rem,5vw,2.5rem);margin-bottom:14px}
  .sec-sub{font-size:1.02rem;max-width:560px;margin:0 auto}

  .bg-blush{background:linear-gradient(180deg,var(--rosa-bebe),#FFF6FA)}
  .bg-white{background:var(--branco)}
  .bg-roxo{background:var(--roxo-escuro);color:#EBDDF7}
  .bg-roxo h1,.bg-roxo h2,.bg-roxo h3{color:#fff}
  .bg-roxo .eyebrow{color:var(--rosa-claro)}

  .btn{display:inline-block;background:var(--verde);color:#fff;font-family:'Quicksand',sans-serif;font-weight:700;font-size:1.08rem;text-decoration:none;border:none;cursor:pointer;padding:18px 44px;border-radius:999px;box-shadow:0 10px 26px rgba(34,197,94,.4);transition:transform .18s ease,box-shadow .18s ease;animation:pulse 2.2s ease-in-out infinite}
  .btn:hover{transform:translateY(-2px)}
  .btn.full{width:100%;text-align:center}
  @keyframes pulse{0%,100%{box-shadow:0 10px 26px rgba(34,197,94,.40),0 0 0 0 rgba(34,197,94,.45)}50%{box-shadow:0 12px 30px rgba(34,197,94,.55),0 0 0 14px rgba(34,197,94,0)}}
  @media (prefers-reduced-motion:reduce){.btn{animation:none}}

  /* HERO */
  .topbar{padding:20px 22px;text-align:center}
  .brandmark{font-family:'Fraunces',serif;font-style:italic;font-weight:500;color:var(--roxo);font-size:1.05rem}
  .hero{padding:34px 22px 72px}
  .hero-grid{display:grid;gap:34px;align-items:center}
  .hero h1{font-size:clamp(2.1rem,7vw,3.4rem);margin-bottom:18px;letter-spacing:-.01em}
  .hero h1 em{font-style:italic;color:var(--rosa-forte)}
  .hero p{font-size:1.12rem;max-width:480px}
  .hero-photo{width:100%;aspect-ratio:1/1;border-radius:var(--blob);box-shadow:var(--sombra-forte);overflow:hidden}
  .hero-img{width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;display:block}
  .scroll-hint{margin-top:26px;font-weight:600;color:var(--roxo);font-size:.92rem;opacity:.8}

  /* PROVA SOCIAL */
  .wpp-grid{display:grid;gap:24px 22px;margin-top:38px}
  .wpp{position:relative;background:#FFEAF1;border-radius:16px 16px 16px 4px;padding:14px 16px 10px;box-shadow:var(--sombra);text-align:left}
  .wpp::after{content:"";position:absolute;left:-7px;bottom:0;width:0;height:0;border:8px solid transparent;border-right-color:#FFEAF1;border-bottom:0;border-left:0}
  .wpp-head{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:9px;margin-bottom:8px}
  .avatar{flex:0 0 36px;width:36px;height:36px;border-radius:50%;overflow:hidden;box-shadow:0 2px 6px rgba(74,42,120,.22)}
  .avatar svg{width:100%;height:100%;display:block}
  .wpp .name{font-weight:700;color:var(--rosa-forte);font-size:.82rem;margin:0}
  .wpp p{font-size:.97rem;color:#4f4060;font-weight:500}
  .wpp .meta{display:block;text-align:right;font-size:.7rem;color:#B58FB0;font-weight:600;margin-top:4px}
  .wpp .ck{color:#34B7F1;letter-spacing:-2px;margin-left:3px}

  /* VOZES */
  .voices{display:grid;gap:14px;margin-top:34px}
  .voice{background:rgba(255,255,255,.06);border-left:3px solid var(--rosa-forte);border-radius:0 14px 14px 0;padding:18px 22px;font-family:'Fraunces',serif;font-style:italic;font-weight:400;font-size:1.12rem;color:#F3E7FB;line-height:1.4}

  /* DIAGNOSTICO */
  .reasons{display:grid;gap:16px;margin-top:32px}
  .reason{background:var(--branco);border-radius:16px;padding:24px;box-shadow:var(--sombra);border:1px solid #F3E2EC}
  .reason h3{font-size:1.18rem;margin-bottom:6px}
  .reason p{font-size:.98rem}
  .punch{margin-top:30px;font-family:'Fraunces',serif;font-weight:600;font-size:1.25rem;color:var(--rosa-forte);text-align:center}
  .compose-photos{display:flex;justify-content:center;margin:26px 0 4px}
  .compose-photos img{width:84px;height:84px;border-radius:50%;object-fit:cover;border:4px solid var(--rosa-bebe);box-shadow:var(--sombra);margin-left:-18px}
  .compose-photos img:first-child{margin-left:0}

  /* PASSOS */
  .steps{position:relative;display:grid;gap:0;margin-top:36px}
  .step{position:relative;display:grid;grid-template-columns:54px 1fr;column-gap:18px;padding-bottom:30px}
  .step:last-child{padding-bottom:0}
  .step .num{position:relative;z-index:2;width:54px;height:54px;border-radius:50%;background:var(--rosa-forte);color:#fff;font-family:'Fraunces',serif;font-size:1.5rem;font-weight:700;line-height:1;display:grid;place-items:center;margin:0}
  .step:not(:last-child)::before{content:"";position:absolute;left:26px;top:58px;bottom:-2px;width:2px;background:rgba(244,217,228,.4);z-index:1}
  .step .stxt{padding-top:5px;text-align:left}
  .step h3{font-size:1.18rem;margin-bottom:6px;color:#fff}
  .step p{font-size:.96rem;color:#E0CFF0}

  /* LISTAS */
  .deliver{display:grid;gap:12px;margin-top:34px}
  .deliver li{list-style:none;display:flex;gap:14px;align-items:flex-start;background:var(--branco);border-radius:14px;padding:16px 20px;box-shadow:var(--sombra);font-weight:600;color:#4f4060}
  .check{flex:0 0 24px;width:24px;height:24px;border-radius:50%;background:#E6F7EC;color:#22A559;display:grid;place-items:center;font-weight:800;font-size:.85rem;margin-top:1px}
  .qual{display:grid;gap:12px;margin-top:32px}
  .qual li{list-style:none;display:flex;gap:13px;align-items:flex-start;font-weight:600;color:#4f4060;background:var(--branco);border-radius:14px;padding:15px 18px;box-shadow:var(--sombra);border:1px solid #F3E2EC}
  .qual-card{margin-top:30px;background:var(--rosa-bebe);border:1px solid var(--rosa-forte);border-radius:16px;padding:22px;text-align:center;font-family:'Fraunces',serif;font-size:1.12rem;color:var(--roxo-escuro);font-weight:500}
  .bg-roxo .qual li{color:#EFE3FA}
  .bg-roxo .qual .check{background:rgba(255,255,255,.12);color:var(--rosa-claro)}
  .bg-roxo .qual-card{background:rgba(217,77,140,.14);color:#fff}

  /* PRECO */
  .price-card{margin:36px auto 0;max-width:460px;background:rgba(255,255,255,.06);border:2px solid var(--rosa-forte);border-radius:24px;padding:38px 30px;text-align:center;box-shadow:0 18px 50px rgba(0,0,0,.25)}
  .price-card .tag{font-family:'Fraunces',serif;font-style:italic;color:var(--rosa-claro);font-size:1.15rem;margin-bottom:14px}
  .price-card .price-cta{font-family:'Fraunces',serif;font-weight:600;color:#fff;font-size:1.3rem;line-height:1.25;margin-bottom:18px}
  .price-card .big{font-family:'Fraunces',serif;font-weight:700;color:#fff;font-size:clamp(3rem,12vw,4.4rem);line-height:1;margin:2px 0 8px}
  .price-card .cash{color:#E0CFF0;font-size:1rem;margin-bottom:26px}
  .price-card .btn{margin-bottom:18px}
  .badges{display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:8px 18px;justify-content:center;font-size:.84rem;color:#D9C7EC;font-weight:600}
  .price-card .parcela{font-family:'Fraunces',serif;color:var(--rosa-claro);font-weight:600;font-size:1.25rem;margin-bottom:6px}
  .oferta-sep .price-card{background:var(--roxo-escuro);border-color:var(--rosa-forte);box-shadow:0 18px 50px rgba(74,42,120,.35)}
  .howbox{max-width:720px;margin:42px auto 0}
  .how-title{color:#fff;text-align:center;font-size:1.45rem;margin-bottom:20px}
  .how-steps{display:grid;gap:14px}
  .how-step{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:16px;background:rgba(255,255,255,.07);border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.14);border-radius:16px;padding:18px 20px}
  .how-n{flex:0 0 44px;width:44px;height:44px;border-radius:50%;background:var(--verde);color:#fff;font-family:'Fraunces',serif;font-weight:700;font-size:1.35rem;display:grid;place-items:center}
  .how-step p{color:#EBDDF7;font-weight:600;font-size:1rem;text-align:left}
  @media(min-width:780px){.how-steps{grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr)}.how-step{flex-direction:column;text-align:center}.how-step p{text-align:center}}

  /* CARTA */
  .letter p{font-size:1.08rem;margin-bottom:18px}
  .letter .lead{font-family:'Fraunces',serif;font-size:1.4rem;color:var(--roxo);font-weight:600;line-height:1.25}

  /* CTA WHATS */
  .btn-whats{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;margin-top:26px;background:var(--roxo);color:#fff;font-family:'Quicksand',sans-serif;font-weight:700;font-size:1.05rem;text-decoration:none;padding:16px 34px;border-radius:999px;box-shadow:0 10px 26px rgba(106,63,160,.32);transition:transform .18s ease,box-shadow .18s ease}
  .btn-whats:hover{transform:translateY(-2px);box-shadow:0 16px 34px rgba(106,63,160,.42)}
  .btn-whats svg{width:22px;height:22px;fill:#fff}

  /* AUTORIDADE */
  .auth-grid{display:grid;gap:20px;align-items:center;margin-top:30px}
  .auth-photo{position:relative;display:flex;justify-content:center}
  .auth-photo::before{content:"";position:absolute;width:80%;aspect-ratio:1;border-radius:var(--blob);bottom:0;background:radial-gradient(circle at 50% 42%, rgba(244,217,228,.30), rgba(244,217,228,0) 70%)}
  .day-img{width:100%;max-width:330px;display:block;position:relative;z-index:1;filter:drop-shadow(0 18px 30px rgba(0,0,0,.32))}
  .auth-bio p{color:#EBDDF7;font-size:1.05rem;margin-bottom:15px}
  .auth-bio p:first-child{font-family:'Fraunces',serif;font-style:italic;color:#fff;font-size:1.2rem;line-height:1.35}

  /* STATS */
  .stats{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(2,1fr);gap:28px 16px;margin:44px auto 4px;max-width:780px}
  .stat{text-align:center}
  .stat-ic{display:inline-flex;width:38px;height:38px;color:var(--rosa-claro);margin-bottom:8px}
  .stat-ic svg{width:100%;height:100%;fill:currentColor}
  .stat-num{display:block;font-family:'Fraunces',serif;font-weight:700;font-size:clamp(1.5rem,5vw,2rem);color:#fff;line-height:1}
  .stat-lbl{display:block;margin-top:4px;font-weight:600;color:#D9C7EC;font-size:.9rem}

  /* FAQ + RODAPE */
  .faq{margin-top:34px;display:grid;gap:12px}
  details{background:var(--branco);border-radius:14px;box-shadow:var(--sombra);border:1px solid #F3E2EC;overflow:hidden}
  summary{list-style:none;cursor:pointer;padding:18px 22px;font-family:'Fraunces',serif;font-weight:600;color:var(--roxo-escuro);font-size:1.02rem;display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;gap:12px}
  summary::-webkit-details-marker{display:none}
  summary::after{content:"+";font-family:'Quicksand';font-weight:700;color:var(--rosa-forte);font-size:1.4rem;transition:transform .2s}
  details[open] summary::after{transform:rotate(45deg)}
  details .ans{padding:0 22px 20px;font-weight:500;color:#5a4a6b}
  footer{background:#3A1F62;color:#C7B3DF;text-align:center;padding:48px 22px;font-size:.86rem;line-height:1.8}
  footer .fbrand{font-family:'Fraunces',serif;font-style:italic;color:#fff;font-size:1.2rem;margin-bottom:6px}
  footer a{color:#E3CFF5;font-weight:700;text-decoration:none}

  .reveal{opacity:0;transform:translateY(18px);transition:opacity .7s ease,transform .7s ease}
  .reveal.in{opacity:1;transform:none}
  @media (prefers-reduced-motion:reduce){.reveal{opacity:1;transform:none;transition:none}}

  @media(min-width:780px){
    .section{padding:96px 32px}
    .hero{padding:46px 32px 96px}
    .hero-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:54px}
    .wpp-grid{grid-template-columns:repeat(2,1fr);gap:22px}
    .reasons{grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:20px}
    .steps{grid-template-columns:repeat(4,1fr);column-gap:24px}
    .step{grid-template-columns:1fr;justify-items:center;text-align:center;padding-bottom:0}
    .step .num{margin-bottom:16px}
    .step .stxt{padding-top:0;text-align:center}
    .step:not(:last-child)::before{display:none}
    .steps::after{content:"";position:absolute;top:26px;left:12.5%;right:12.5%;height:2px;background:rgba(244,217,228,.4);z-index:0}
    .deliver{max-width:760px;margin-left:auto;margin-right:auto}
    .qual{grid-template-columns:repeat(2,1fr);gap:14px}
    .auth-grid{grid-template-columns:0.85fr 1.15fr;gap:40px}
    .auth-bio{text-align:left}
    .stats{grid-template-columns:repeat(4,1fr)}
  }
  @media(min-width:1040px){.steps{column-gap:36px}}
</style>

<style id="tema-final">
:root{--rosa-bebe:#1B2746;--rosa-claro:#F4C9DC;--rosa-forte:#FF8FB6;--roxo:#CBD6F2;--roxo-escuro:#1E2A4A;--texto-claro:#E5E2EC;--texto-titulo:#FBF6FB;--branco:#121A30;}
body{background:#161E36;color:#E5E2EC}
.bg-blush{background:linear-gradient(180deg,#1B2746,#161E36)}
.bg-white{background:#121A30;color:#E5E2EC}
.bg-roxo{background:#1E2A4A;color:#E9EAF4}
.sec-title{color:#FBF6FB}.sec-sub{color:#BCC2D6}
.hero h1{color:#FBF6FB}.hero h1 em{color:#FF8FB6}
.hero p,.scroll-hint{color:#BEC4D8}
.eyebrow,.bg-roxo .eyebrow{color:#FF92BE}
.reason{background:rgba(255,255,255,.05);border-color:rgba(255,143,182,.20)}
.reason h3{color:#FF9EC4}.reason p{color:#CDD2E2}
.qual li,.deliver li{background:rgba(255,255,255,.05);border-color:rgba(255,143,182,.16);color:#DCDFEC}
.qual-card{background:rgba(255,143,182,.12);border-color:rgba(255,143,182,.4);color:#FBF6FB}
.wpp{background:rgba(255,255,255,.06)}.wpp::after{border-right-color:rgba(255,255,255,.06)}
.wpp .name{color:#FF9EC4}.wpp p{color:#DCDFEC}.wpp .meta{color:#9AA4C0}
.stat-num{color:#FBF6FB}.stat-lbl{color:#BEC4D8}.stat-ic{color:#FF92BE}
.price-card{background:rgba(255,255,255,.04)}
.price-card .price-cta,.price-card .big{color:#FBF6FB}.price-card .cash{color:#C7CFE6}.price-card .parcela{color:#FF9EC4}
.badges{color:#BEC4D8}
.how-step p{color:#DCE2F2}.how-title{color:#fff}
details{background:rgba(255,255,255,.045);border-color:rgba(255,255,255,.08)}
summary{color:#EFEAF2}summary::after{color:#FF92BE}details .ans{color:#BCC0D2}
.letter .lead{color:#FF9EC4}.letter p{color:#CDD2E2}
.brandmark{color:#FF92BE}.btn-whats{background:#1E2A4A}
footer{background:#121A30;color:#9AA4C0}

/* botao de compra: verde + pulsando */
.btn{background:#21C161;color:#06331b;box-shadow:0 12px 28px rgba(33,193,97,.40);animation:pulsa 1.8s ease-in-out infinite}
.btn:hover{transform:translateY(-2px) scale(1.03);box-shadow:0 16px 40px rgba(33,193,97,.55)}
@keyframes pulsa{0%,100%{transform:scale(1)}50%{transform:scale(1.045)}}
@media(prefers-reduced-motion:reduce){.btn{animation:none}}

/* bonus com peso + iconografia */
.bonus-grid{display:grid;gap:16px;margin-top:30px;text-align:left}
@media(min-width:680px){.bonus-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr}}
.bonus-card{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:16px;background:rgba(255,255,255,.055);border:1px solid rgba(255,143,182,.28);border-radius:18px;padding:20px 22px;box-shadow:0 10px 30px rgba(10,16,34,.25)}
.bonus-ic{flex:0 0 auto;width:50px;height:50px;border-radius:14px;display:grid;place-items:center;background:rgba(255,143,182,.14);color:#FF9EC4}
.bonus-ic svg{width:27px;height:27px}
.bonus-tt{font-family:'Fraunces',serif;font-weight:600;font-size:1.06rem;color:#FBF6FB;line-height:1.32}
.bonus-tag{display:inline-block;margin:0 0 6px;font-family:'Quicksand',sans-serif;font-size:.6rem;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:.14em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#06331b;background:#21C161;padding:3px 9px;border-radius:6px}
</style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- DOBRA 1 : HEADLINE -->
<section class="hero bg-blush">
  <div class="wrap hero-grid">
    <div class="reveal">
      <span class="eyebrow">Guia da Pega</span>
      <h1>Amamentar dói? Existe um jeito de facilitar a pega para o seu bebê, e a dor pode ir embora <em>já na próxima mamada</em>.</h1>
      <p>Sem fissura, sem bico de silicone, com a certeza de que ele está mamando de verdade e ficando satisfeito.</p>
      <div class="scroll-hint">role para entender ↓</div>
    </div>
    <div class="hero-photo reveal"><img class="hero-img" src="data:image/jpeg;base64," alt="Mãe amamentando o bebê no colo"></div>
  </div>
</section>


<!-- SITUAÇÕES -->
<section class="section bg-roxo">
  <div class="narrow center">
    <h2 class="sec-title reveal">Você está vivendo alguma dessas situações?</h2>
    <div class="voices">
      <p class="voice reveal">A amamentação dói, e toda mamada já começa com aquele aperto só de pensar.</p>
      <p class="voice reveal">Seu bico é pequeno, plano ou invertido, e o bebê escorrega na hora de pegar.</p>
      <p class="voice reveal">Apareceu um calo ou bolha no lábio do bebê.</p>
      <p class="voice reveal">As mamadas são longas e parecem não ter fim.</p>
      <p class="voice reveal">Ele larga o peito e em pouco tempo já quer de novo, parece que nunca sacia.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="qual-card reveal" style="margin-top:30px">Se você se identificou, fica tranquila. Não é culpa sua, nem do seu bebê, e muito menos do seu leite. Seu bebê só precisa de ajuda para pegar o seio de uma maneira que o fará mamar com mais facilidade.</div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- EXISTE UM CAMINHO -->
<section class="section bg-white">
  <div class="wrap center">
    <span class="eyebrow reveal">Existe um caminho</span>
    <h2 class="sec-title reveal">Tem um jeito de ofertar o peito para o bebê que deixa todos esses problemas para trás</h2>
    <p class="sec-sub reveal">Em poucos minutos você vai aprender a deixar a amamentação confortável para os dois. A partir daí:</p>
    <ul class="deliver" style="text-align:left">
      <li class="reveal"><span class="check">✓</span> O bebê extrai mais leite em menos tempo</li>
      <li class="reveal"><span class="check">✓</span> Os lábios dele ficam relaxados, por isso os calos cicatrizam e não voltam</li>
      <li class="reveal"><span class="check">✓</span> Ele fica saciado por mais tempo e aumenta o intervalo entre as mamadas</li>
      <li class="reveal"><span class="check">✓</span> A dor vai embora, mesmo com o seio machucado, porque o bebê passa a sugar do jeito que não machuca</li>
    </ul>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- DOBRA 11 : AUTORIDADE -->
<section class="section bg-roxo">
  <div class="wrap center">
    <span class="eyebrow reveal">Quem vai te ensinar</span>
    <h2 class="sec-title reveal">Dayane Dos Anjos</h2>
    <p class="sec-sub reveal">Consultora de amamentação, sono e cuidados com o bebê</p>
    <div class="auth-grid">
      <div class="auth-photo reveal"><img class="day-img" src="data:image/png;base64," alt="Dayane Dos Anjos, consultora de amamentação"></div>
      <div class="auth-bio reveal">
        <p>As primeiras semanas decidem o sucesso da amamentação, mas é justamente quando a mãe fica sozinha, sem uma orientação clara e objetiva. Quando a dor, a insegurança e o cansaço tomam conta, o desmame precoce acaba ganhando espaço em muitas famílias.</p>
